        <p class="text-[11px] text-emerald-700/70 dark:text-emerald-400/70 leading-relaxed uppercase font-medium tracking-wide">
            Tokens are derived from the Web Crypto API's cryptographically secure random number generator (CSPRNG). 
            They are suitable for session IDs, CSRF tokens, and permanent API keys.
        </p>
    </div>
  </div>
